else if (n <1600) → Division3
else if ( ... ) → Division2

So the missing condition is (n <= 1899). So the else if should check if n is less than or equal to 1899. So the code would be:

else if (n <= 1899) {
   Console.WriteLine("Division 2");
}

That way, any n that is 1600-1899 falls into Division2, and anything higher (1900 and above) goes to Division1.
